    Grimlock looked Kenzo over and shrugged, "Me Grimlock lookf for rest of
crew. Me got bored smacking on doors so me wait in mess hall for bots to
show up. Me Grimlock like new strategy." Nodding briefly the bot made his
way past Kenzo to continue headingtowards the mess hall.
